Zamfara Governor Bello Matawalle has approved the suspension of Emir of Dansadau, Alhaji Hussaini Umar with immediate effect.  He said District Head of Dansadau, Alhaji Nasiru Muhammad S/Kudu, should oversee the affairs of the Emirate.  The Governor also suspended District Head of Nasarawa Mailayi Alhaji Bello Wakkala. His suspension is also with immediate effect. No reason was given for the suspensions. The Governor approved a high-powered committee to investigate activities of the suspended monarchs. The Committe members comprise DIG Moh’d Ibrahim Tsafe (rtd) as Chairman; Hon. Yusuf Alhassan Kanoma,Hon. Ibrahim T Tukur, Sheikh Ahmad Umar Kanoma , Sheikh Abdullahi Umar Dalla Dalla ,Sheikh Kabir Umar Maru as members while Barr Abdurrashid Haruna will serve as Secretary.  Source By Abubakar AhmedGusau - The Zamfara Government has announced the immediate suspension of a first class traditional ruler, the Emir of Maru, Alhaji Abubakar Ibrahim, over alleged involvement with bandits in the state.The suspension is contained in a statement signed by Mr Yusuf Idris, Director-General to the governor on Press… In "News" Abuja (Sundiata Post) - Governor of Zamfara state, Muhammad Matawalle has approved the suspension of Emir of Maru, Alhaji Abubakar Cika Ibrahim and District Head of Kanoma Alhaji Yahaya Mohammed. The  suspensions which takes immediate effect was announced yesterday in a statement signed by the Director General, Press Affairs to… In "Top Stories" Governor Bello Matawalle of Zamfara State has dethroned the Emir of Maru, Abubakar Chika and the District Head of Kanoma, Lawal Ahmed for supporting bandits. The move has been hailed by the Arewa Consultative Forum who lauded Governor Bello Matawalle of Zamfara State for sacking the Emir of Maru, Abubakar… In "Features"